{"tid":1790180,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來失望到極點係呢種感覺","createTime":"2019-12-19T22:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T06:17:15.000Z","uid":209242,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef88006b0aee88cd1e188b161bc566eb7316ecaa","tid":1790180,"uid":209242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T22:43:36.000Z","msg":"望住部電腦 打緊機<br />\n會係咁流眼淚<br />\n成個腦空白晒<br />\n時間流得好慢<br />\n淨係想消失<br />\n<br />\n生日都係食普通茶記Hea過<br />\n因為我真係好重視聖誕節，<br />\n尤其今年聖誕本身可以同啊爸講聲聖誕快樂<br />\n而家人都走咗，唔知點講，<br />\n只係想男朋友工作上面請個假陪我過一日，<br />\n點知佢話唔想請假，第二日補祝<br />\n我都係想25號好好地陪住自己...<br />\n<br />\n而家25號獨自去聖誕Suck Uou遊行算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQOM3Cp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUQOM3Cp.png&h=c8371cc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7e73093a2e57c5e6c77daf03fd000e3509894ab","tid":1790180,"uid":113934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T22:46:27.000Z","msg":"頂住呀<br />\n聖誕一定有好多人陪你一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果頂唔順就休息一下先啦"},{"pid":"dccd3eeef76b39ba232eb2ff031677c51785da93","tid":1790180,"uid":209242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7e73093a2e57c5e6c77daf03fd000e3509894ab","tid":1790180,"uid":113934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T22:46:27.000Z","msg":"頂住呀<br />\n聖誕一定有好多人陪你一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果頂唔順就休息一下先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T22:49:18.000Z","msg":"個心好似穿咗窿咁<br />\n同佢講又覺得我無理取鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d987687df62fbd3d6b5acca541dc5c6883929df2","tid":1790180,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T23:14:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7983429c0e90d1544db9f739927305e7e2914f3f","tid":1790180,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-1